Overview
In this project I implment an encryption system that interacts through the driver program
This program contains a logger program, encryption program, and the driver program

Logger program : Logs the activity in a specific format
Encyrption program :  encrypt and decrypt strings
Driver program : the main interface, where  user can interact with logger and encryption

To run the project execute this line in the terminal:
python3 driver.py logfile.txt

User Commands
Password: Allows you to enter a new passkey or pick a preveisly used string.
Encrypt: Encrypt the strings by using the passkey
Decrypt: Decrypt the string by using the passkey
history: stores the strings
quit: termintates the system